    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/766370/extras/26a1a179e289ab689bf334dca08a2f35.avif?t=1684279119\" width=600 height=98 /></span><br><br>进入一块丧尸横行的区域，并为了成为最后的幸存者，与其他11名玩家而展开较量——也可以组队一起为了生存而战。收集武器、摧毁丧尸巢穴可升级，综合利用你的高端跑酷和无情战斗技巧与对手斗智斗勇并赢得胜利。<br><br>进入一块丧尸横行的区域，为了成为最后的幸存者，12名玩家展开较量。收集武器、摧毁丧尸巢穴可升级，综合利用你的跑酷和战斗技巧战胜对手。进去的人里只有一人能活着出来。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/766370/extras/1256b0c3b5b00118adaef38b853e0fa8.webp?t=1684279119\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>击杀感染者并摧毁它们的巢穴可收集血样并升级。猎杀其他玩家，偷走他们的血样，并成为唯一的幸存者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/766370/extras/fde5a9a213313c57fd6ff8713424c618.poster.avif?t=1684279119\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/766370/extras/fde5a9a213313c57fd6ff8713424c618.webm?t=1684279119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/766370/extras/fde5a9a213313c57fd6ff8713424c618.mp4?t=1684279119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/766370/extras/2f4af792d0864e649b8370db7a4e6b2d.webp?t=1684279119\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>当你在逃命、追击其他玩家或朝直升机飞奔时，你的跑酷技巧能让你占上风。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/766370/extras/c811232bb64bb489c72344962ec58855.poster.avif?t=1684279119\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/766370/extras/c811232bb64bb489c72344962ec5885